> x bench

> x bench

A Victorian public bench made from cast iron and wooden slats. A small boy is sat on the bench looking miserable, you recognise him as Kevin, he lives on your street.
> x Kevin

> x Kevin

An 8 year old boy called Kevin, you recognise him as he lives on your street. He has blonde-brown hair and is wearing a thick red jumper, khaki trousers and a white bobble hat. He looks fed-up.
> talk to Kevin

> talk to Kevin

"Hello", says Kevin, "I'm not supposed to talk to strangers, but I recognise you from our street." "My parents have gone away for a few days, and 'accidently' left me home alone again". "It would be OK, but I've seen some dodgy guys hanging around town in a van. I overheard them talking about burglary." "Perhaps you could do something about them, else I'll be forced to take rather drastic measures!" Kevin fixes you with a grin of pure mischief.
> ask Kevin about dodgy guys

> ask Kevin about dodgy guys

"Yeah they were parked outside my house. They were talking about coming back tonight to rob my house!"
