You are in Chester Street.

You can see a Dodgy Looking Van.

You can go in, east or west.

You are outside Your House on a side road near the city centre, that runs from East to West.

The daylight is waning and there is a strange looking star in the western sky.

It's crisp and cold, and in the distance you can hear carol singing.

> x van

> x van

A knackered pale blue Dodge Ram van, with a large bore exhaust pipe. It has 'Oh-Kay Plumbing and Heating' written on the side. There appears to be a row of snowglobes on the inside front windowsill.
> x pipe

> x pipe

The van has a large boy racer style exhaust pipe. Large enough that one could block it with a suitably placed item.
> put potato in pipe

> put potato in pipe

You glance around to make sure no one is watching then shove the potato firmly into the exhaust pipe, it forms a good seal.

At that moment you spy two dodgy men entering Chester Street, making sure they don't see you stand further down the street.

The dodgy men open the van and get in, you can hear them bickering, "Marv you are an idiot with a big mouth, let's hide this van away and come back later when the kid's asleep".

You hear the van start up and there is a high-pitched whining sound coming from the exhaust that increases in pitch. The driver guns the engine and there is loud *KA-BOOM!!" explosion that destroys the back half of the van, blasts the bonnet into the air and sends a potato whistling past your ear at supersonic speed.

The two men stumble out of the van with their clothes steaming and smoking from the heat of the explosion. The short fat one says, "Let's get the hell out of here! If the cops arrive I'll have to try and explain away your damn snow globe collection! One from each house we've robbed. You idiot Marv!"

They disappear up the street leaving the van's smoking ruins behind.

> look

> look

